{
  "stem": "9110.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And after, when they came to Warsaw, the Germans, my sister came from-- they thought we were all dead-- from Bialobrzegi.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She came to Warsaw, walking and hitchhiking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And she found us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that time, we went home to our town with the baby and my sister.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And my brother-in-law stayed in Warsaw because he had to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He had a factory.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And that-- that was when they came in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But later, it was a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "My father had to come home, because he usually was in the woods always.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "For the summer I used to go stay with him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He just came home for Saturday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So he started to teach children Hebrew, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I started to bake bread.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I was kneading maybe, 50 pounds of flour.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I wasn't afraid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I used to go across the SS.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They didn't recognize me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "My sister, if she had to bring to somebody a bread, she was so scared that they could've recognized her right away, that she's hiding something.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this went on for a long time-- for a long time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my other sister went back to Warsaw when they closed the Warsaw ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it started to be very bad in our town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So one time, I hear-- when they put us in the ghetto, I hear a knock on the door.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to the door to open.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So right away, I got two whips.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where's the man?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where's the man?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The SS.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't have a husband.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I have an old father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was 52.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He looked so old.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he walked in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He gave my father a few whips.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
